OL,3,CChanges in farming: Can family farms
OL,4,Creally survive?
OL,6,FComing from a farming background, I've
OL,7,Fseen first-hand what the industry
OL,8,Flooks like today and the struggles
OL,9,Ffarmers are facing.
OL,11,FOur countryside used to be a patchwork
OL,12,Fof small, family farms: lots of
OL,13,Ffarmers doing lots of manual work.
OL,14,FThings are different now. Technology
OL,15,Fhas done away with some jobs but
OL,16,Ffarmers face global competition.
OL,17,F'Small' won't earn you a living. Not
OL,18,Funless you find another income to go
OL,19,Fwith it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
