OL,3,CChanges in farming: Can family farms
OL,4,Creally survive?
OL,6,FSpeaking to Hugh, Celia and Josh Gay,
OL,7,Fit surprised me just how much of their
OL,8,Fincome is from their farm shop and
OL,9,Fcafe rather than their farm itself.
OL,10,FFive-sixths, to be precise! The only
OL,11,Fway they've kept their small farm
OL,12,Fgoing is by opening another business.
