OL,3,CChanges in farming: Can family farms
OL,4,Creally survive?
OL,6,FThen there are solar panels - more and
OL,7,Fmore of them are appearing on green
OL,8,Ffields as farmers try to make their
OL,9,Fland pay. For Patrick Twigger on his
OL,10,Ffarm near Frome, renting out 46 acres
OL,11,Ffor solar panels generates a reliable
OL,12,Fincome stream for his family. He feels
OL,13,Fhe has a right to a living from his
OL,14,Fland, even if some of his neighbours
OL,15,Fvoiced objections.
OL,17,FDiversification - be it solar panels,
OL,18,Ffarm shops, or even pumpkin picking -
OL,19,Fis the key to financial survival.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
