OL,3,CChanges in farming: Can family farms
OL,4,Creally survive?
OL,6,FEven the dairy cows wear 'smart
OL,7,Fcollars' to track their eating,
OL,8,Fdrinking and reproductive cycles.
OL,9,FBritish dairy producers have dropped
OL,10,F70% in 30 years. Only super-efficient
OL,11,Ffarms like Harry's can cut it
OL,12,Ffinancially.
OL,14,FBut Harry's farm looks positively
OL,15,Ftraditional compared to the vertical
OL,16,Ffarm near Lydney. Going inside was a
OL,17,Fsweaty experience to say the least -
OL,18,F26 degrees!
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
