OL,3,CChanges in farming: Can family farms
OL,4,Creally survive?
OL,6,FThis is plant heaven - the
OL,7,Ftemperature, light wavelength,
OL,8,Fhumidity and nutrition are all perfect
OL,9,Ffor them, and the energy used is
OL,10,Frenewable.
OL,12,FNo wonder the lettuce we saw can go
OL,13,Ffrom seed to supermarket in 14 days.
OL,14,FVertical farms save space and speed up
OL,15,Fgrowth. But it's hard to see them
OL,16,Fbeing an economical way to grow big
OL,17,Fcrops - the grains, potatoes and rice
OL,18,Fthat the UK's 68 million people depend
OL,19,Fon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
